title: FRAM Ultra Synthetic Automotive Replacement Oil Filter, Designed for Synthetic Oil Changes Lasting up to 20k Miles, XG10575 with SureGrip (Pack of 1)
description: FRAM Ultra Synthetic Oil Filter XG10575 helps get top performance from newer engines and provide maximum protection for older ones. Engineered for all motor oil types, Ultra Synthetic Oil Filters have the ultimate dual-layer synthetic media which provides up to 20,000 miles of engine protection. This high capacity, high efficiency filter delivers peak performance. No matter what you drive, or what motor oil you use, FRAM has a filter for you.
